\begin_layout Standard
One long term goal for our research groups is to study plasmonic systems
 with strong light-matter couplings where Raman scattering is a very sensitive
 probe of the collective behavior of electronic dynamics.
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "sukharev_optics_2017"
