\end_layout

\end_inset

We denote the rescaling operator for the EM fields by:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
{\cal R}\left[\delta U_{R}^{fi}\right]:\left(\begin{array}{c}
\mathbf{E}_{S}\\
\mathbf{B}_{S}
\end{array}\right)\rightarrow\left(\begin{array}{c}
\mathbf{E}_{S}+\alpha^{fi}\delta\mathbf{E}_{R}^{fi}\\
\mathbf{B}_{S}+\beta^{fi}\delta\mathbf{B}_{R}^{fi}
\end{array}\right).\label{eq:rescaling_operator}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where the rescaling coefficients are chosen to be
\begin_inset Formula 
